## Farzana's Picks by Buyer Type

**Best overall halo:** [Falling Edge Pavé Diamond Halo in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-311113?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,410 · 368 reviews. The most-reviewed halo on Blue Nile. The falling edge cascade is the design detail that separates this from a generic round halo — it has a reason and it reads that way in person.

**Best for oval centers:** [Pavé Diamond Halo in 14K White Gold (Oval)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-oval-by-james-allen-item-311125?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,565. Outstanding value for an oval center. The halo adds 15–20% apparent size to an oval that already reads larger than a round of the same carat weight.

**Best for vintage buyers:** [Diamond Filigree Vintage-Style in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-filigree-vintage-style-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-304462?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,275 · 228 reviews. 228 reviews on a vintage design at this price point is exceptional. If you want vintage, this is the data-backed choice.

**Best for rose gold buyers:** [Round Split Band Diamond Halo in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-split-band-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-314977?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $4,400 · 210 reviews. If the budget allows, the split band in rose gold is the most photographed halo design in this catalog. 210 reviews says buyers keep choosing it.

**Best budget halo:** [Pavé Halo (Cushion/Emerald/Radiant) in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-cushion-emerald-radiant-by-james-allen-item-314929?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,320. Lowest setting price in the catalog. Works for cushion, emerald, and radiant centers. 69 reviews confirms this isn't an obscure pick.

**Best for pear centers:** [Pavé Diamond Halo (Pear) in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-pear-by-james-allen-item-311119?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,360 · 91 reviews. Halo protection on the pear tip is structurally important, not just aesthetic. This is the correct way to set a pear center.

